data.description: Beautifully updated home, move in ready. 2 living, 2 dining. The bedrooms are large and spacious. The playhouse w/swings, slide and a climbing wall stays with the house. There is a shed in the backyard, and a floored attic for lots of extra storage space.  The master bath and the upstairs bath both feature double sinks.
data.whatILove: The second living area is located on the upstairs landing and give the kids their own area. The master bedroom is on the first level. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and has been updated with granite counter tops and tile/glass back splash. The 1/2 bath has been updated with a new tall toilet and hardware. The master bath has been updated with new onyx counter tops, new faucets, onyx shower walls, and a shower tower. The entire first level is all tile, the second level is carpeted with the exception of the second level bathroom. The neighborhood is quiet with long standing residents. The HOA is not expensive at only $100 yearly. The area is up and coming with lots of options for shopping and movies. Everything you need is within a 5 mile range. The Broken Arrow School system is ranked the best in Oklahoma.
